variables.name: APPEARANCE_UNKNOWN
variables.comment: A constant describing cervical mucus which appearance is unknown.

variables.name: APPEARANCE_DRY
variables.comment: A constant describing a dry cervical mucus.

variables.name: APPEARANCE_STICKY
variables.comment: A constant describing a sticky cervical mucus.

variables.name: APPEARANCE_CREAMY
variables.comment: A constant describing creamy like looking cervical mucus.

variables.name: APPEARANCE_WATERY
variables.comment: A constant describing watery like looking cervical mucus.

variables.name: APPEARANCE_EGG_WHITE
variables.comment: A constant describing clear or egg white like looking cervical mucus.

variables.name: APPEARANCE_UNUSUAL
variables.comment: A constant describing an unusual (worth attention) kind of cervical mucus.
